=The Demon=

2
00:01:00,587 --> 00:01:03,250
=Episode 17=

3
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,439
Cat Demon?

4
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:35,719
It's really you.

5
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,000
Who are you?

6
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:41,920
Dayao!

7
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,879
Where have you been?

8
00:01:44,359 --> 00:01:46,280
I've been looking for you!

9
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,079
A half-demon?

10
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:51,319
If you want a duel, let's just have one.

11
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,239
Cut the crap.

12
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:53,599
What a joke.

13
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,200
You've been doing evil for a century.

14
00:01:55,359 --> 00:01:56,159
And now you're

15
00:01:56,159 --> 00:01:57,280
doing humanity harm

16
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,519
with this half-human and half-demon.

17
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,079
You're dead meat!

18
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:01,840
A half-demon?

19
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,079
Momo.

20
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:16,280
I've heard about half-demons.

21
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:21,199
A half-demon is the result
of a human and a demon's union.

22
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:30,639
And they're not able
to enhance their spiritual power.

23
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,680
Hear me out, Momo.

24
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:33,400
No matter how hard I work,

25
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,479
petty tricks

26
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:39,639
are all I can manage.

27
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,360
Thus...

28
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,319
It's not that

29
00:02:48,319 --> 00:02:50,400
you're reluctant
to make me the Guardian.

30
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,240
I just can't be one.

31
00:02:58,319 --> 00:02:59,120
Momo!

32
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,919
You busybody!

33
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,479
Fan Dayao.

34
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,639
Run.

35
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,120
Step aside!

36
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,960
He's my master.

37
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,039
If you want to fight him,

38
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:21,080
defeat me first.

39
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:22,879
You think I dare not do that?

40
00:03:22,879 --> 00:03:24,120
Of course you'd dare to do it.

41
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,479
But I think

42
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:27,719
you should go find Miss Rong first.

43
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,240
Just you wait.

44
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,520
I've cast the Heartless Spell on you.

45
00:03:55,479 --> 00:03:57,039
Whenever you think of her,

46
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,919
your heart will be in bone-eroding pain.

47
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:02,680
Things won't end well

48
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,759
if you fall in love with a demon.

49
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:06,840
Master.

50
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,520
No matter
what her past lifetime was like,

51
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,560
