63
00:04:43,910 --> 00:04:44,759
I'm getting you out of here.

64
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:45,680
Go away!

65
00:04:50,079 --> 00:04:51,240
Are you really going to stay here

66
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,079
and witness his wedding?

67
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,560
So what if I am?

68
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:57,439
If you're here to catch demons,

69
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,800
