the cause of all the trouble.

95
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:29,000
By then,

96
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,079
Shen Wangchen will be

97
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:30,959
in deep water,

98
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:33,240
getting despised and reprimanded
by everyone in the city.

99
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,759
All this has nothing to do with me.

100
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,000
I think

101
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,759
